channel.title: Enso II | RS2011 - Requesting a Website Developer (Community Manager)
channel.description:
Hello. [B][U] How you can contact me?[/U][/B] [B]By using Skype; NEXONLTD[/B]
[B]I'm basically looking for a person who can handle IP.Board forums well, you don't need to be skilled with programming at all.[/B] I will be also handling the whole server part. But the fact is that i'm in the military so I have no time to manage website. Also if you're accepted you instantly become a community manager with developer rights.
What's Enso? Incredible RS2011 RSPS, with insane amount of content and will most likely be a very successful private server.
Media [img]http://puu.sh/7FaFP.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/7EPnq.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/7w573.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/7uOUs.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/7xoex.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/5LiSF.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/5cY3Q.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/5l2Id.jpg[/img]
Enso is a real 667 loading 667, and has a very promising future for a RSPS. [B] Kind regards, Fuzen Seth.[/B]
